item.title: 北京时代二保焊机 TDN 3500 MAG/MIG/CO2 焊电源使用说明书
item.description: During the introduction of Co2 Arch Welding last week, it was my harddest interpretation. I was new to the equipment and so were the trainees. There were no reference material so It was hard understanding how the machine operated. So over the weekend I seerched on the Manufacturers website where I came accross the manual, but in Chinese.
